                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A little madness in the Spring</l>
                    <l>Is wholesome even for the King,</l>
                    <l>But God be with the Clown,</l>
                    <l>Who ponders this tremendous scene --</l>
                    <l>This whole experiment of green,</l>
                    <l>As if it were his own!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
